('HP:0004328', 'Abnormal anterior eye segment morphology', 'An abnormality of the anterior segment of the eyeball (which comprises the structures in front of the vitreous humour: the cornea, iris, ciliary body, and lens).'),
('HP:0004329', 'Abnormal posterior eye segment morphology', ''),
