('HP:0012567', 'Premature epimetaphyseal fusion in ulna', 'Stop of growth at the epiphyseal plate the hyaline cartilage plate in the metaphysis at one or more long bones in the ulna, at an earlier than normal age, resulting in growth arrest and shortening of the involved bone.'),
