('HP:0012670', 'Orthostatic syncope', 'Syncope following a quick change in position from lying down to standing.'),
('HP:0012671', 'Abulia', 'Poverty of behavior and speech output, lack of initiative, loss of emotional responses, psychomotor slowing, and prolonged speech latency.'),
('HP:0012672', 'Akinetic mutism', 'Akinetic mutism is essentially characterized by a total absence of spontaneous behavior and speech occurring in the presence of preserved visual tracking.'),
('HP:0012673', 'Aplasia of the upper vagina', 'A failure to develop of the upper vagina.'),
