('HP:0040006', 'Mortality/Aging', ''),
('HP:0040007', 'Absent pigmentation of chest', 'Lack of skin pigmentation (coloring) of the chest.'),
('HP:0040008', 'Aplasia of facial bones', ''),
('HP:0040009', 'Hyperparakeratosis', 'Abnormal keratinization of the epidermal stratum coreum (horny layer) with increased keratin formation, preservation of the nuclei in the superficial cells, and absence of the stratum granulosum.'),
('HP:0040010', 'Small posterior fossa', ''),
('HP:0040011', 'Flat posterior fossa', ''),
('HP:0040012', 'Chromosome breakage', 'Elevated rate of chromosomal breakage or interchanges occurring either spontaneously or following exposure to various DNA-damaging agents. This feature may be assayed by treatment of cultured lymphocytes with agents such as chemical mutagens, irradiation, and alkylating agents.'),
